<div id="pips-content">	  

<div id="brand-title"><h1><a href="../../../latejunction">Late Junction</a></h1></div>








<div id="episode-title"><h3>29 September 2006</h3></div>






<div id="broadcast-instance"><p>Friday 29 September 2006 22:30-0:00 (Radio 3)</p></div>




<div id="episode-description"><p>Live from the Fruitmarket in Glasgow, Verity Sharp hosts a special programme of words and music reflecting the range of Radio 3's output over the last 60 years. With live music from The Perfect Houseplants and I Fagiolini. Plus specially-commissioned poetry to mark the anniversary.</p></div>




<div id="programme">
<h5>Duration:</h5>
<p>1 hour 30 minutes</p>
</div>


	







































